ref=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι\">ι</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Quotient.mk\">⟦</a><span class=\"fn\">x</span><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Quotient.mk\">⟧</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι_apply","kind":"theorem","line":90,"name":"FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι_apply","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L90-L90"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι_surjective\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">WickAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">ι_surjective</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Function.html#Function.Surjective\">Function.Surjective</a> <span class=\"fn\">⇑<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι\">ι</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι_surjective","kind":"theorem","line":85,"name":"FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι_surjective","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L85-L88"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">WickAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">ι</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Hom.html#AlgHom\">→ₐ[</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Hom.html#AlgHom\">]</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra\">WickAlgebra</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, `ι` is defined as the projection\n\n`𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra →ₐ[ℂ] 𝓕.WickAlgebra`\n\ntaking each element of `𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra` to its equivalence class in `WickAlgebra 𝓕`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι","kind":"def","line":72,"name":"FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L72-L83"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.equiv_iff_exists_add\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">WickAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">equiv_iff_exists_add</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x </span><span class=\"fn\">y</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#HasEquiv.Equiv\">≈</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Iff\">↔</a> <span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span>), <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/TwoSidedIdeal/Operations.html#TwoSidedIdeal.span\">TwoSidedIdeal.span</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.fieldOpIdealSet\">fieldOpIdealSet</a></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.equiv_iff_exists_add","kind":"theorem","line":64,"name":"FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.equiv_iff_exists_add","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L64-L70"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.equiv_iff_sub_mem_ideal\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">WickAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">equiv_iff_sub_mem_ideal</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x </span><span class=\"fn\">y</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#HasEquiv.Equiv\">≈</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Iff\">↔</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSub.hSub\">-</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/TwoSidedIdeal/Operations.html#TwoSidedIdeal.span\">TwoSidedIdeal.span</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.fieldOpIdealSet\">fieldOpIdealSet</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.equiv_iff_sub_mem_ideal","kind":"theorem","line":59,"name":"FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.equiv_iff_sub_mem_ideal","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L59-L62"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.instSetoidFieldOpFreeAlgebra\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">WickAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">instSetoidFieldOpFreeAlgebra</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Setoid\">Setoid</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The instance of a setoid on `FieldOpFreeAlgebra` from the ideal `TwoSidedIdeal`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.instSetoidFieldOpFreeAlgebra","kind":"instance","line":56,"name":"FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.instSetoidFieldOpFreeAlgebra","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L56-L57"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">WickAlgebra</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, the algebra `𝓕.WickAlgebra` is defined as the quotient\n  of the free algebra `𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra` by the ideal generated by\n- `[ofCrAnOpF φc, ofCrAnOpF φc']ₛF` for `φc` and `φc'` field creation operators.\n  This corresponds to the condition that two creation operators always super-commute.\n- `[ofCrAnOpF φa, ofCrAnOpF φa']ₛF` for `φa` and `φa'` field annihilation operators.\n  This corresponds to the condition that two annihilation operators always super-commute.\n- `[ofCrAnOpF φ, ofCrAnOpF φ']ₛF` for `φ` and `φ'` operators with different statistics.\n  This corresponds to the condition that two operators with different statistics always\n  super-commute. In other words, fermions and bosons always super-commute.\n- `[ofCrAnOpF φ1, [ofCrAnOpF φ2, ofCrAnOpF φ3]ₛF]ₛF`. This corresponds to the condition,\n  when combined with the conditions above, that the super-commutator is in the center\n  of the algebra.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra","kind":"def","line":38,"name":"FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L38-L51"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.fieldOpIdealSet\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">fieldOpIdealSet</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The set contains the super-commutators equal to zero in the operator algebra.\nThis contains e.g. the super-commutator of two creation operators. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.fieldOpIdealSet","kind":"def","line":25,"name":"FieldSpecification.fieldOpIdealSet","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L25-L36"}}],"imports":["Init","PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.SuperCommute","Mathlib.Algebra.RingQuot","Mathlib.RingTheory.TwoSidedIdeal.Operations"],"instances":[{"className":"Setoid","name":"FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.instSetoidFieldOpFreeAlgebra","typeNames":["FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra"]}],"name":"PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.WickAlgebra.Basic"}